overview: Founded in 1978 by Connie Tompkins, A Travel Resource and Group Travel Specialists has worked within the travel industry for over 26 years. This depth of experience allows you the traveler to take advantage of the latest technology to discover the best value available. We will research ALL of the best options for either you or your group. Our international network of contacts are dedicated to a simple and effective philosophy; provide the best value at the lowest cost, with the least amount of complications.
